<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="take-note-of">take note of</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-notice">1.<strong>注意 (notice)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Next time you chat with a friend, take note of how you’re sitting.  
下次你和朋友聊天时，注意一下你的坐姿。</p><footer>2008 湖南改</footer></div></div>